# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:4467
msgid "<ulink url=\"&regularexpressions;\">Regular expressions</ulink> are used in many text processing tools.  They are analogous to the shell globs, but they are more complicated and powerful."
msgstr "Les <ulink url=\"&regularexpressions;\">expressions rationnelles</ulink> sont utilises avec de nombreux outils de traitement du texte. Elles sont analogues aux motifs gnriques &nbsp;globs&nbsp; du shell mais elles sont plus compliques et plus puissantes."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:4468
msgid "The regular expression describes the matching pattern and is made up of text characters and <emphasis role=\"strong\">metacharacters</emphasis>."
msgstr "L'expression rationnelle dcrit le motif de correspondance, elle est constitue de caractres de texte et de <emphasis role=\"strong\">mta-caractres</emphasis>."

