# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:7049
msgid "In reality, it is not so easy to get meaningful understanding quickly out from these logs.  See <xref linkend=\"_recording_changes_in_configuration_files\"/> for easier way."
