# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:13220
msgid "Instead of manually choosing configuration as described in <xref linkend=\"_the_manually_switchable_network_configuration\"/>, you can use the mapping mechanism described in <xref linkend=\"_the_mapping_stanza\"/> to select network configuration automatically with custom scripts."
msgstr "Plutt que de choisir manuellement la configuration comme il est dcrit dans la <xref linkend=\"_the_manually_switchable_network_configuration\"/>, vous pouvez utiliser le mcanisme de cartographie rseau dcrit dans la <xref linkend=\"_the_mapping_stanza\"/> pour slectionner automatiquement la configuration du rseau  l'aide de scripts personnaliss."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:13221
msgid "The <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>(8) command provided by the <literal>guessnet</literal> package is designed to be used as a mapping script and provides powerful framework to enhance the <literal>ifupdown</literal> system."
msgstr "La commande <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>(8) fournie par le paquet <literal>guessnet</literal> est conue pour tre utilise comme script de cartographie rseau et fournit une infrastructure puissante pour amliorer le systme <literal>ifupdown</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:13225
msgid "You list test condition as the value for <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> options for each network configuration under <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> stanza."
msgstr "Vous listez la condition de test comme valeur des options de <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> pour chacune des configurations de rseau de l'entre <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis>."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:13230
msgid "Mapping choses the <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> with first non-ERROR result as the network configuration."
msgstr "La cartographie du rseau choisit la premire entre <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> donnant un rsultat qui ne soit pas en erreur comme configuration du rseau."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:13234
msgid "This dual usage of the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file by the mapping script, <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>, and the original network configuration infrastructure, <literal>ifupdown</literal>, does not cause negative impacts since <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> options only export extra environment variables to scripts run by the <literal>ifupdown</literal> system.  See details in <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>(8)."
msgstr "Cette double utilisation du fichier &nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp; par le script de mapping, <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal> et l'infrastructure d'origine de configuration du rseau, <literal>ifupdown</literal>, n'a pas d'impact ngatif car les options de <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> n'exportent que des variables d'environnement supplmentaires vers les scripts lancs par le systme <literal>ifupdown</literal>.  Voir <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>(8) pour davantage d'informations."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:13236
msgid "When multiple <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> option lines are required in \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\", use option lines started with <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet1</literal></emphasis>, <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet2</literal></emphasis>, and so on, since the <literal>ifupdown</literal> package does not allow starting strings of option lines to be repeated."
msgstr "Lorsqu'il est ncessaire d'avoir plusieurs lignes d'options de <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> dans &nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;, utilisez les lignes d'options commenant  par <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet1</literal></emphasis>, <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet2</literal></emphasis> et ainsi de suite, car le paquet <literal>ifupdown</literal> n'autorise pas que les chanes de caractres de dbut des lignes d'options soient dupliques."

