#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18370
msgid "Some programs consume more memory after supporting I18N.  This is because they are coded to use <ulink url=\"&utfdcucse;\">UTF-32(UCS4)</ulink> internally to support Unicode for speed optimization and consume 4 bytes per each ASCII character data independent of locale selected.  Again, you loose nothing by deploying UTF-8 locale."
msgstr "Certains programmes utilisent davantage de mmoire lors de l'utilisation de I18N. Ceci parce qu'ils sont cods avec l'utilisation interne d'<ulink url=\"&utfdcucse;\">UTF-32(UCS4)</ulink> pour la prise en compte d'Unicode afin d'optimiser la vitesse, ils utilisent 4 octets pour chaque caractre ASCII indpendamment de la &nbsp;locale&nbsp; slectionne. De nouveau, il n'y a rien  perdre en mettant en uvre des paramtres linguistiques UTF-8."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18371
msgid "The vendor specific old non-UTF-8 encoding systems tend to have minor but annoying differences on some characters such as graphic ones for many countries.  The deployment of the UTF-8 system by the modern OSs practically solved these conflicting encoding issues."
msgstr "Les anciens systmes de codage propritaires non UTF-8 tendent  avoir une diffrence mineure mais ennuyeuse pour certains caractres tels que les caractres graphiques pour de nombreux pays. La mise en uvre du systme UTF-8 sur les systmes d'exploitation modernes a pratiquement rsolu ces problmes de codage conflictuels."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18374
msgid "The reconfiguration of the locale"
msgstr "Reconfiguration des paramtres linguistiques"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18375
msgid "In order for the system to access a particular locale, the locale data must be compiled from the locale database. (The Debian system does <emphasis role=\"strong\">not</emphasis> come with all available locales pre-compiled unless you installed the <literal>locales-all</literal> package.) The full list of supported locales available for compiling are listed in \"<literal>/usr/share/i18n/SUPPORTED</literal>\". This lists all the proper locale names.  The following lists all the available UTF-8 locales already compiled to the binary form."
msgstr "Pour accder  un paramtre linguistique particulier, les donnes de paramtres linguistiques doivent tre compiles dans la base de donnes des paramtres linguistiques. (Le systme Debian n'est <emphasis role=\"strong\">pas</emphasis> distribu avec tous les paramtres linguistiques prcompils   moins que vous n'ayez install le paquet <literal>locales-all</literal>). La liste complte des paramtres linguistiques pris en charge pour tre compils se trouve dans &nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/i18n/SUPPORTED</literal>&nbsp;. On y trouve la liste de tous les noms des &nbsp;locale&nbsp;. La commande ci-aprs affiche la liste de tous les paramtres linguistiques UTF-8 dj compils sous forme binaire&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18376
#, no-wrap
msgid "$ locale -a | grep utf8"
msgstr "$ locale -a | grep utf8"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18377
msgid "The following command execution reconfigures the <literal>locales</literal> package."
msgstr "L'excution de la commande suivante va reconfigurer le paquet <literal>locales</literal>&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18378
#, no-wrap
msgid "# dpkg-reconfigure locales"
msgstr "# dpkg-reconfigure locales"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18379
msgid "This process involves 3 steps."
msgstr "Ce processus se droule en trois tapes&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18383
msgid "Update the list of available locales"
msgstr "mettre  jour la liste des paramtres linguistiques disponibles&nbsp;;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18388
msgid "Compile them into the binary form"
msgstr "les compiler sous forme binaire&nbsp;;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18393
msgid "Set the system wide default locale value in the \"<literal>/etc/defaults/locale</literal>\" for use by PAM (see <xref linkend=\"_pam_and_nss\"/>)"
msgstr "dfinir la valeur des paramtres linguistiques par dfaut pour l'ensemble du systme dans &nbsp;<literal>/etc/defaults/locale</literal>&nbsp; pour une utilisation par PAM (voir <xref linkend=\"_pam_and_nss\"/>)."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18397
msgid "The list of available locale should include \"<literal>en_US.UTF-8</literal>\" and all the interesting languages with \"<literal>UTF-8</literal>\"."
msgstr "La liste des paramtres linguistiques disponible devra comporter &nbsp;<literal>fr_FR.UTF-8</literal>&nbsp; et toutes les langues intressantes avec &nbsp;<literal>UTF-8</literal>&nbsp;."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18398
msgid "The recommended default locale is \"<literal>en_US.UTF-8</literal>\" for US English.  For other languages, please make sure to chose locale with \"<literal>UTF-8</literal>\".  Any one of these settings can handle any international characters."
msgstr "Pour l'anglais des USA, le paramtre linguistique recommands est &nbsp;<literal>en_US.UTF-8</literal>&nbsp;. Pour les autres langues, assurez-vous de bien choisir une valeur avec &nbsp;<literal>UTF-8</literal>&nbsp; (NdT&nbsp;: prendre &nbsp;<literal>de_FR.UTF-8</literal>&nbsp; pour la langue franaise en France) . Les caractres internationaux sont tous pris en charge par l'un quelconque de ces paramtrage."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18400
msgid "Although setting locale to \"<literal>C</literal>\" uses US English message, it handles only ASCII characters."
msgstr "Bien que le paramtre linguistique &nbsp;<literal>C</literal>&nbsp; utilise des messages en anglais, il ne prend en compte que les caractres ASCII."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><table><tgroup><thead><row><entry>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18404
msgid "The value of the \"<literal>$LANG</literal>\" environment variable"
