#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18405
msgid "The value of the \"<literal>$LANG</literal>\" environment variable is set and changed by many applications."
msgstr "La valeur de la variable d'environnement &nbsp;<literal>$LANG</literal>&nbsp; est dfinie et modifie par de nombreuses applications."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18409
msgid "Set initially by the PAM mechanism of <literal>login</literal>(1) for the local Linux console programs"
msgstr "Elle est dfinie au dpart par le mcanisme PAM de <literal>login</literal>(1) pour les programmes de console locale de Linux"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18414
msgid "Set initially by the PAM mechanism of the display manager for all X programs"
msgstr "Elle est dfinie au dpart par le mcanisme PAM du gestionnaire d'affichage pour tous les programmes X"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18419
msgid "Set initially by the PAM mechanism of <literal>ssh</literal>(1) for the remote console programs"
msgstr "Elle est dfinie au dpart par le mcanisme PAM de<literal>ssh</literal>(1) pour les programmes de la console distante"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18424
msgid "Changed by some display manager such as <literal>gdm</literal>(1) for all X programs"
msgstr "Modifi par certains gestionnaire d'affichage tels que <literal>gdm</literal>(1) pour tous les programmes X"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18429
msgid "Changed by the X session startup code via \"<literal>~/.xsessionrc</literal>\" for all X programs (<literal>lenny</literal> feature)"
msgstr "Modifis par le code de dmarrage de la session X par l'intermdiaire de &nbsp;<literal>~/.xsessionrc</literal>&nbsp; pour tous les programmes X (fonctionnalit de <literal>lenny</literal>)"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18434
msgid "Changed by the shell startup code, e.g. \"<literal>~/.bashrc</literal>\", for all console programs"
msgstr "Modifi par le code de dmarrage de l'interprteur de commandes, par exemple &nbsp;<literal>~/.bashrc</literal>&nbsp;, pour tous les programmes de console"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18439
msgid "It is good idea to install system wide default locale as \"<literal>en_US.UTF-8</literal>\" for maximum compatibility."
msgstr "C'est une bonne ide de dfinir les paramtres linguistiques par dfaut pour l'ensemble du systme  &nbsp;<literal>en_US.UTF-8</literal>&nbsp; pour un maximum de compatibilit."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18443
msgid "Specific locale only under X Window"
msgstr "Paramtre linguistique spcifique sous X Window"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18444
msgid "You can chose specific locale only under X Window irrespective of your system wide default locale using PAM customization (see <xref linkend=\"_pam_and_nss\"/>) as follows."
msgstr "Vous pouvez choisir vos paramtres linguistiques spcifiques sous X Window indpendamment de leur valeur par dfaut valable pour l'ensemble du systme en utilisant une personnalisation de PAM (voir <xref linkend=\"_pam_and_nss\"/>) comme suit&nbsp;:."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18445
msgid "This environment should provide you with your best desktop experience with stability.  You have access to the functioning character terminal with readable messages even when the X Window System is not working.  This becomes essential for languages which use non-roman characters such as Chinese, Japanese, and Korean."
msgstr "Cet environnement devrait vous apporter la meilleure exprience d'environnement de bureau stable. Vous avez accs  un terminal en mode caractres fonctionnel avec des messages lisibles mme lorsque le systme X Window ne fonctionne pas. Ceci devient essentiel pour des langues qui utilisent des caractres non romains tels que le chinois, le japonais et le coren."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18447
msgid "There may be another way available as the improvement of X session manager package but please read following as the generic and basic method of setting the locale.  For <literal>gdm</literal>(1), I know you can select the locale of X session via its memu."
msgstr "Il peut exister une autre manire comme l'amlioration du paquet de gestion de session de X mais veuillez lire ce qui suit qui est la mthode gnrique et basique pour dfinir les paramtres linguistiques. Pour <literal>gdm</literal>(1), je sais que l'on peut slectionner la &nbsp;locale&nbsp; de la session X par l'intermdiaire de son memu."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18449
msgid "The following line defines file location of the language environment in the PAM configuration file, such as \"<literal>/etc/pam.d/gdm</literal>."
msgstr "La ligne suivante dfinit l'emplacement du fichier de l'environnement de langue dans le fichier de configuration de PAM, tels que &nbsp;<literal>/etc/pam.d/gdm</literal>&nbsp;&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18450
#, no-wrap
msgid "auth    required        pam_env.so read_env=1 envfile=/etc/default/locale"
msgstr "auth    required        pam_env.so read_env=1 envfile=/etc/default/locale"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18451
msgid "Change this to the following."
msgstr "Modifiez-la avec ce qui suit&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
