msgstr "Astuces du systme"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18489
msgid "Here, I describe basic tips to configure and manage systems, mostly from the console."
