#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26012
msgid "You may wish to set several global configuration in \"<literal>~/.gitconfig</literal>\" such as your name and email address used by Git by the following."
msgstr "Vous pourrez dfinir certains lments de configuration globaux, comme votre nom et votre adresse de courriel utilise par Git, dans &nbsp;<literal>~/.gitconfig</literal>&nbsp; de la manire suivante&nbsp;:"

