#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:28936
msgid "The de facto image file format of the digital camera is the <ulink url=\"&exchangeableimagefileformat;\">Exchangeable Image File Format</ulink> (EXIF) which is the <ulink url=\"&jpeg;\">JPEG</ulink> image file format with additional metadata tags.  It can hold information such as date, time, and camera settings."
msgstr "Le format standard de fait pour les images d'appareils photo numriques est <ulink url=\"&exchangeableimagefileformat;\">Exchangeable Image File Format</ulink> (EXIF) qui est compos d'une image au format <ulink url=\"&jpeg;\">JPEG</ulink>  laquelle sont ajouts des balises de mta-donnes. Il peut contenir des informations telles que la date, l'heure ou les paramtres de l'appareil photo."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:28937
msgid "<ulink url=\"&thelempelzivwelcsdatacompression;\">The Lempel-Ziv-Welch (LZW) lossless data compression</ulink> patent has been expired.  <ulink url=\"&graphicsinterchangeformatgif;\">Graphics Interchange Format (GIF)</ulink> utilities which use the LZW compression method are now freely available on the Debian system."
msgstr "Le brevet de compression de donnes sans pertes <ulink url=\"&thelempelzivwelcsdatacompression;\">Lempel-Ziv-Welch (LZW)</ulink> est arriv en fin de validit. Les utilitaires du format <ulink url=\"&graphicsinterchangeformatgif;\">Graphics Interchange Format (GIF)</ulink> qui utilise la mthode de compression LZW peuvent tre maintenant librement disponibles sur un systme Debian."

